{
  "video_id": "l32m1nGxVw4",
  "title": "Should There Be a Universal Basic Income?",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 6200.0,
      "end_time": 8670.0,
      "text": "Today&#39;s topic comes from viewer Armando, who writes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 8670.0,
      "end_time": 11140.0,
      "text": "what&#39;s going on with universal basic income?"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 11140.0,
      "end_time": 13600.0,
      "text": "Yes, it&#39;s true that Switzerland plans"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 13600.0,
      "end_time": 15960.0,
      "text": "to vote on a guaranteed basic income for all adults--"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 15960.0,
      "end_time": 20350.0,
      "text": "about 2,500 francs, which amount to about 2,800 a month."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 20350.0,
      "end_time": 21990.0,
      "text": "That idea might seem far-fetched,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 21990.0,
      "end_time": 24290.0,
      "text": "but a bigger conversation about income"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 24300.0,
      "end_time": 26210.0,
      "text": "is happening not just in Switzerland, but all"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 26210.0,
      "end_time": 26860.0,
      "text": "over the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 26860.0,
      "end_time": 29340.0,
      "text": "In the US, President Obama said in a speech"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 29340.0,
      "end_time": 31860.0,
      "text": "this week that he is making income inequality"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 31860.0,
      "end_time": 34220.0,
      "text": "a priority for the next three years."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 34220.0,
      "end_time": 38000.0,
      "text": "The combined trends of increased inequality and decreasing"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 38000.0,
      "end_time": 40570.0,
      "text": "mobility pose a fundamental threat"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 40570.0,
      "end_time": 42810.0,
      "text": "to the American dream, our way of life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 42810.0,
      "end_time": 45500.0,
      "text": "and what we stand for around the globe."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 45500.0,
      "end_time": 47660.0,
      "text": "The US federal minimum is $7.25 an hour,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 47660.0,
      "end_time": 50590.0,
      "text": "which amounts to about $15,000 a year."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 50600.0,
      "end_time": 52350.0,
      "text": "Most states also have minimum wage laws."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 52350.0,
      "end_time": 54860.0,
      "text": "The highest is Washington, at $9.19 an hour."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 54860.0,
      "end_time": 57564.0,
      "text": "And some states have lower than federal or no minimum."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 57564.0,
      "end_time": 59105.0,
      "text": "And you don&#39;t have to be an economist"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 59105.0,
      "end_time": 62169.0,
      "text": "to know that $7.25 doesn&#39;t get you too far anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 62170.0,
      "end_time": 65540.0,
      "text": "The real value of $7.25 an hour, adjusting for inflation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 65540.0,
      "end_time": 67770.0,
      "text": "has depreciated over the past forty years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 67770.0,
      "end_time": 70600.0,
      "text": "according to the National Employment Law Project."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 70600.0,
      "end_time": 73310.0,
      "text": "And employees of Walmart, which is the largest private employer"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 73310.0,
      "end_time": 75980.0,
      "text": "in the US, recently held Black Friday protests"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 75980.0,
      "end_time": 79620.0,
      "text": "asking for wage increases and better workplace conditions."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 79620.0,
      "end_time": 81430.0,
      "text": "And on Thursday, fast food workers"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 81430.0,
      "end_time": 85300.0,
      "text": "staged a nationwide strike to protest unlivable wages,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 85300.0,
      "end_time": 86500.0,
      "text": "in the words of the people I spoke"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 86500.0,
      "end_time": 88600.0,
      "text": "with in Oakland, California."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 88600.0,
      "end_time": 90780.0,
      "text": "And I work as a shift leader."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 90780.0,
      "end_time": 92900.0,
      "text": "I get paid $9.25 an hour."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 92900.0,
      "end_time": 94780.0,
      "text": "I am full time."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 94780.0,
      "end_time": 95755.0,
      "text": "And I do struggle."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 95755.0,
      "end_time": 97920.0,
      "text": "And to this day, I&#39;m still struggling."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 97920.0,
      "end_time": 100680.0,
      "text": "I get food stamps."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 100680.0,
      "end_time": 102330.0,
      "text": "And I can&#39;t afford my rent."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 102330.0,
      "end_time": 104760.0,
      "text": "And sometimes I have to tell my landlady, can she"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 104760.0,
      "end_time": 107720.0,
      "text": "wait for my rent, because I&#39;m a single mother with three"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 107720.0,
      "end_time": 108420.0,
      "text": "babies."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 108420.0,
      "end_time": 113320.0,
      "text": "I am a crew member and a crew trainer."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 113320.0,
      "end_time": 115830.0,
      "text": "And I worked there for about two years."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 115830.0,
      "end_time": 117789.0,
      "text": "And I make about $8.26."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 117790.0,
      "end_time": 119670.0,
      "text": "And I haven&#39;t seen any raises."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 119670.0,
      "end_time": 120850.0,
      "text": "My hours have been cut."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 120850.0,
      "end_time": 122470.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s unfair to workers."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 122470.0,
      "end_time": 123750.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s unfair to moms."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 123750.0,
      "end_time": 125350.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s unfair to people trying to get"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 125350.0,
      "end_time": 126600.0,
      "text": "on their own two feet like me."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 126600.0,
      "end_time": 129780.0,
      "text": "So the overall question is, how much do people need to live?"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 129780.0,
      "end_time": 132780.0,
      "text": "A pending bill called the fair minimum wage act is aiming"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 132780.0,
      "end_time": 135520.0,
      "text": "to raise the federal minimum to $10.10 an hour."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 135520.0,
      "end_time": 137660.0,
      "text": "And until that happens, if it happens,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 137660.0,
      "end_time": 139250.0,
      "text": "the debate is sure to continue."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 139250.0,
      "end_time": 141150.0,
      "text": "Be sure to weigh in the comments with your opinion."
    },
    {
